            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1679407175284-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1679407175284-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tofu karaage</strong> with your <strong>cooked rice</strong>, <strong>slaw</strong> and <strong>miso mayo dip</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> over the rice and scatter your <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> over everything</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
